{"title":"谚语","authors":["贺祥"],"dates":[{"year":1961,"month":6,"day":9}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"谚语"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好问的人迷不了路。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"闭着眼捉不住麻雀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不调查做不好工作。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不下水，一辈子不会游泳。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不扬帆，一辈子不会驾船。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"涉浅水者得鱼虾，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"涉深水者得蛟龙。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人心越实越好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"火心越空越好。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"泥人经不起雨打，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"假话经不起调查。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"闻而不审，不若无闻。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"贺祥辑"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}